trans-unit.source: Represents an object that arranges contextual tab groups in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa un objeto que organiza los grupos de pestañas contextuales en <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Ribbon" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: The size that the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" /> needs to position its child elements.
trans-unit.target: Tamaño que <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" /> necesita para poder colocar los elementos secundarios.

trans-unit.source: Positions and sizes the child elements in this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonContextualTabGroup" />.
trans-unit.target: Coloca y ajusta el tamaño de los elementos secundarios en este recuadro <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.RibbonContextualTabGroup" />.

trans-unit.source: The actual size of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.
trans-unit.target: Tamaño real de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: The maximum size of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.
trans-unit.target: Tamaño máximo de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: Measures the child elements in this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" /> in preparation of arranging them during the <see cref="M:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel.ArrangeOverride(System.Windows.Size)" /> pass.
trans-unit.target: Mide los elementos secundarios de este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" /> para prepararlos para su organización durante la fase <see cref="M:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel.ArrangeOverride(System.Windows.Size)" />.

trans-unit.source: The desired size of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.
trans-unit.target: Tamaño deseado de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.DrawingContext" /> object to draw.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.DrawingContext" /> que se va a dibujar.

trans-unit.source: Draws the content of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.DrawingContext" /> object during the render pass of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" /> element.
trans-unit.target: Dibuja el contenido de un objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.DrawingContext" /> durante la fase de representación de un elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Ribbon.Primitives.RibbonContextualTabGroupsPanel" />.
